{"sn22.114:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 22.114 ","sn22.114:0.2":"12. Dhammakathikavagga ","sn22.114:0.3":"Vijjasutta ","sn22.114:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn22.114:1.2":"Ekamantam nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn22.114:1.3":"“‘vijja, vijja’ti, bhante, vuccati. ","sn22.114:1.4":"Katama nu kho, bhante, vijja; ","sn22.114:1.5":"kittavata ca vijjagato hoti”ti? ","sn22.114:1.6":"“Idha, bhikkhu, sutava ariyasavako rupam pajanati, rupasamudayam … rupanirodham … rupanirodhagaminim patipadam pajanati. ","sn22.114:1.7":"Vedanam … ","sn22.114:1.8":"sannam … ","sn22.114:1.9":"sankhare pajanati …pe… ","sn22.114:1.10":"vinnananirodhagaminim patipadam pajanati. ","sn22.114:1.11":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhu, vijja; ","sn22.114:1.12":"ettavata ca vijjagato hoti”ti. ","sn22.114:1.13":"Dutiyam. "}